ed, as WordPress continues to update its own code in the upcoming releases.'=>'This may report many entries from WordPress itself. This is expected, as WordPress continues to update its own code in the upcoming releases.','Detect and log deprecations in the default WordPress version of jQuery'=>'Detect and log deprecations in the default WordPress version of jQuery','Capture modern deprecations'=>'Capture modern deprecations','Show deprecation notices, on each admin page, as they happen'=>'Show deprecation notices, on each admin page, as they happen','Live deprecations'=>'Live deprecations','You can only change jQuery versions in WordPress 5.6 or later'=>'You can only change jQuery versions in WordPress 5.6 or later','jQuery versionLegacy 1.12.4-wp'=>'Legacy 1.12.4-wp','jQuery versionDefault from WordPress'=>'Default from WordPress','jQuery Version'=>'jQuery Version','Clear logs'=>'Clear logs','The following are deprecations logged from the front-end of your site, or while live deprecation notices were disabled in the admin area.'=>'The following are deprecations logged from the front end of your site, or while live deprecation notices were disabled in the admin area.','Theme: %s'=>'Theme: %s','Plugin: %s'=>'Plugin: %s','Inline code, unknown file location'=>'Inline code, unknown file location','Undetermined'=>'Undetermined','Admin deprecation noticesTriggered on page'=>'Triggered on page','Admin deprecation noticesFile location'=>'File location','Admin deprecation noticesPlugin or theme'=>'Plugin or theme','The following deprecations have been logged from the front-end of your site, or from your admin area while live deprecation notices were disabled.'=>'The following deprecations have been logged from the front end of your site, or from your admin area while live deprecation notices were disabled.','There have been no reported deprecations logged in the past week, maybe you no longer need this plugin?'=>'There have been no reported deprecations logged in the past week, maybe you no longer need this plugin?','This is a weekly summary of the warnings still present on your site, relating to the jQuery library. These errors should be addressed as soon as possible.'=>'This is a weekly summary of the warnings still present on your site, relating to the jQuery library. These errors should be addressed as soon as possible.','You can view captured and logged deprecations at %s'=>'You can view captured and logged deprecations at %s','This happened because you, or a visitor to your site, viewed a page that was using one or more deprecated jQuery features which are no longer in use. As the feature being used is no longer maintained, this caused an error. In order to maintain the expected user experience, this automatic downgrade was performed.'=>'This happened because you, or a visitor to your site, viewed a page that was using one or more deprecated jQuery features which are no longer in use. As the feature being used is no longer maintained, this caused an error. In order to maintain the expected user experience, this automatic downgrade was performed.','This is a one-time, automated, message to inform you that the jQuery version on your site has been automatically downgraded to the legacy 1.12.4-wp version.'=>'This is a one-time, automated, message to inform you that the jQuery version on your site has been automatically downgraded to the legacy 1.12.4-wp version.','Greetings!'=>'Greetings!','You are using a WordPress version prior to 5.5.1. This plugin also helps with a bug found in WordPress 5.5.0. Please update WordPress to version 5.5.1, or later, before deactivating this plugin.'=>'You are using a WordPress version prior to 5.5.1. This plugin also helps with a bug found in WordPress 5.5.0. Please update WordPress to version 5.5.1, or later, before deactivating this plugin.','This means you should still check that things work as expected after you have disabled the plugin, and if you know there have been warnings in the admin