dated your plugins and themes, and there are no more warnings, please deactivate Enable jQuery Migrate Helper.','This plugin, called Enable jQuery Migrate Helper, is not a fix. It is a temporary solution to give your plugin and theme authors time to update.'=>'This plugin, called Enable jQuery Migrate Helper, is not a fix. It is a temporary solution to give your plugin and theme authors time to update.','Right now, you are using a plugin to support some old code in this website’s jQuery JavaScript library. That code is deprecated, meaning it is basically obsolete and is losing the support of your themes and plugins and WordPress itself.'=>'Right now, you are using a plugin to support some old code in this website’s jQuery JavaScript library. That code is deprecated, meaning it is basically obsolete and is losing the support of your themes and plugins, and WordPress itself.','Please make sure you are using the latest version of all of your plugins, and your theme. If that is the case, then you may want to ask the developers of the code mentioned in your warnings to update it.'=>'Please make sure you are using the latest version of all of your plugins, and your theme. If that is the case, then you may want to ask the developers of the code mentioned in your warnings to update it.','(Previously known: %1$d Discovered on this page: %2$s)'=>'(Previously known: %1$d. Discovered on this page: %2$s)','jQuery Migrate %s'=>'jQuery Migrate %s','No deprecations have been logged on this site in a while, you may no longer need this plugin.'=>'No deprecations have been logged on this site in a while, you may no longer need this plugin.','No deprecations have been logged'=>'No deprecations have been logged','Admin deprecation noticesPage'=>'Page','Admin deprecation noticesNotice'=>'Notice','Admin deprecation noticesTime'=>'Time','This page generated the following warnings:'=>'This page generated the following warnings:','enable-jquery-migrate-helperWarnings encountered'=>'Warni